Author: basic_throwawayy
Text: We don’t celebrate thanksgiving in NZ. What’s it like? Is it winter? Why is there so much focus on “leftovers”? Do you guys really have decorative food that you can’t eat, like pumpkins and corn etc? Do you guys celebrate Christmas as well? I have so many questions

Author: throwawaythanks364
Text: I felt weirdly fine with thanksgiving until I went to see my therapist. Which is why I am back posting here now...
